snippet: OLNICK--Sylvia. The Palm Beach Country Club expresses its profound sorrow at the passing of its esteemed member Sylvia Olnick, and extends sincere sympathy to her daughters Barbara Lane and Nancy Latainer and other members of her family. Jeffrey B. Lane, President Warren Spector, Club Secretary 1/3
